Thanks. We've had terrific success with Uncharted 3,

49
00:05:28,386 --> 00:05:32,969
and even though I'm not going to put too much focus on the Uncharted games today,

50
00:05:32,969 --> 00:05:37,251
I'll tell you about some of the playtesting techniques later on

51
